<article>
  <section class="statement">
    <div>
      <span class="pink xlarge bold">Teaching is&hellip;</span>
    </div>

    <div>
      <span class="pink medium bold">
        <ul class="slashed-list">
          <li>generation-shaping</li>
          <li>innovative</li>
          <li>life-changing</li>
        </ul>
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-s">Find your future career</h2>

    <p>
      Choosing a career can be a daunting prospect. How do we know what somethings like if we've never done it before?
    </p>

    <p>
      Teaching is a career that changes lives through every generation. Find out if you have that spark.
    </p>
  </section>

  <%= render SubjectSpecific::TextBlockWithTwoImagesComponent.new(
    heading: "Explore teaching advisers",
    colour: "pink",
    image_1_path: "media/images/content/hero-images/0017.jpg",
    image_1_alt: "A teacher sitting with a student helping them with a maths problem",
    image_2_path: "media/images/content/hero-images/0024.jpg",
    image_2_alt: "A maths teacher standing at the front of a full classroom delivering a lesson",
  ) do %>

    <p>
      All our advisers are experienced teachers who can help you gain an insight into the world of teaching.
    </p>

    <p>
      You can talk to them as little or as much as you'd like. They're there to help you.
    </p>
  <% end %>

  <section>
    <figure>
      <blockquote class="pink-quotes">
        <p class="bold">
          I promise the level of satisfaction is like nothing youâ€™ll get in another job. I wake up every morning and want to get into school.
        </p>
      </blockquote>

      <figcaption>Phil, teacher</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

  <section class="columns">
    <div>
      <h2 class="heading-s">What explore teaching advisers can do</h2>

      <p>
        Your adviser can help you:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <ul class="badges">
        <li class="badge">understand what teaching is really like</li>
        <li class="badge">connect with other students</li>
        <li class="badge">build your confidence and transferable skills</li>
        <li class="badge">get classroom experience</li>
        <li class="badge">understand the process to become a teacher</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-s">How to get an explore teaching adviser</h2>

    <p>
        To be eligible for an explore teaching adviser, you just need:
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li>
        to be studying for an undergraduate degree
      </li>
      <li>
        an interest in teaching
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      And that's it!
    </p>
    <p class="call-to-action__action">
      <a href="https://adviser-getintoteaching.education.gov.uk/?channel=222750047">Get an <span>adviser</span></a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <%= render SubjectSpecific::TextBlockWithOneImageComponent.new(
    heading: "Is teaching right for me?",
    colour: "yellow",
    image_path: "media/images/content/hero-images/0009.jpg",
    image_alt: "A teacher standing at the front of her classroom teaching a class",
  ) %>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-s">Use your subject passion</h2>

    <p>
    If you're passionate about a subject, you can bring that to life in front of a classroom of pupils. Help them be inspired by it just like you.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="/blog/the-head-of-science-inspiring-students-in-blackpool">Find out how Jessica brings her passion for science to life in the classroom</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

    <section>
    <h2 class="heading-s">Join a community</h2>

    <p>
    Teaching is about more than just what happens in the classroom. You become part of a school community, alongside fellows teachers and support staff.
    </p>
        <p>
      <a href="/blog/the-fellowship-of-teachers">Explore the friendship Mike and Phil have made outside of the classroom</a>.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2 class="heading-s">Keep learning</h2>

    <p>
      Learning doesn't end once you've passed your teacher training. You'll have the opportunity to further develop your skills through a range of training and qualifications.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="/train-to-be-a-teacher/subject-knowledge-enhancement">
        Find out about national professional qualifications.
      </a>
    </p>
  </section>
